Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唷 來得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.65,0:00:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的店還是這麼冷清
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上生意好得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那張照片是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.39,0:00:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,介紹起來可有點複雜了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.42,0:00:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AmuSphere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它算是用於大規模線上遊戲的NERvGear後繼機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(283,425)}MMO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼也是和SAO一樣的虛擬實境大規模線上遊戲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(393,425)}VRMMO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.81,0:00:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ALf...heim．Online？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是唸做「阿爾普海姆」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是「精靈之國」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精靈...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精靈國度嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是和平系遊戲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你可就錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是超級技能制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重視玩家的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且鼓勵PK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超級技能制？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是沒有所謂的「等級」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可以反覆使用來提升各種技能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥時是依照玩家的運動能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這確實很難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是沒有劍技但有魔法的SAO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在可是大受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是因為能夠「飛行」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能飛...？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是精靈所以有翅膀嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面搭載了飛行引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,習慣後不需要搖桿就可以自由飛翔了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼控制翅膀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過聽說相當困難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要操縱人類沒有的翅膀嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是要透過背後的肌肉來控制嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咳！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個大人氣遊戲跟亞絲娜有什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很像...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也這麼覺得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點告訴我 這到底是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在這遊戲裡面...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ALfheim Online裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡稱為「世界樹」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這棵樹上面有一座傳說中的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩家現在的目標是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比其他種族先一步到達樹木上方的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用飛的不就可以到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說有滯空時間的限制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是有五個玩家按照身高順序疊羅漢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用火箭脫離的方式飛過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然蠢但不失為一個好方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然最後連世界樹最下面的樹枝都沒有到達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他們拍了許多照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而其中一張卻照到了很奇怪的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳥籠？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後將這個鳥籠照片放大到極限後...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是眼前的這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:04:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼亞絲娜會在這裡...？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,RECT製造？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(308,425)}RECT．progress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日奈生命的延續都是靠我維持著的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾基爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個遊戲能借我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是沒關係啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要親眼確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種不用擔心死亡的遊戲對我來說太輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要先去買遊戲機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用NERvGear就可以玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AmuSphere只是NERvGear的強化安全版而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要救出亞絲娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然我們的戰鬥就永遠無法結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後找機會在這裡辦個網聚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給妳！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還、還以為死定了...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真是不小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃東西不要這麼急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小直 關於昨天的事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃...嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,託小直的福我才能打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要救出亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:06:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想見見亞絲娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們一定會成為好朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我先進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚儀式在一週後的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1月26日的這個病房舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屆時也會邀請你來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請再一次...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把力量借給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始連線！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:00.19,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(207,221)\b0\fs27}語言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:00.19,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(395,237)\b0\fs27}日語
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到ALfheim Online！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到ALfheim Online！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先請輸入性別和角色名稱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你就是那個英雄桐人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(287,217)\frz5}桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後 請確認種族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請從這裡選擇種族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就選這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您選擇守衛精靈嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(330,425)}Spriggan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,角色容貌會隨機生成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問您同意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來會將您傳送到守衛精靈的領地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好運
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:46.78,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20\fade(300,0)\pos(322,385)}阿爾普海姆．中立區域．古森林
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來這種地方了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明才經歷過那些事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 這裡是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.81,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,66)\org(428,70)\frz7.925}選項
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.81,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz10.05\pos(435,146)}幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:24.40,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz10.05\pos(446,229)}登出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:25.67,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz9.233\pos(228,64)}警告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:25.67,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(392,130)\frz7.773}在練功區無法即時登出。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:25.67,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz8.93\pos(290,179)}您確定嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 能力數值呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系統BUG嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟SAO的熟練度數值一樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是SAO嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:57.62,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(244,181)}裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:57.62,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(243,257)}道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:57.62,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(242,335)}技能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:10:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要有...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊...結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還認得我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我終於見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇蹟...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說...這裡不是在SAO裡面了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是叫阿爾普海姆的另一個遊戲世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(272,425)}ALfheim Online
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是SAO伺服器的備份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,備份...？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主要程式群與圖檔形式完全相同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過Cardinal系統的版本有點舊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:19.65,defination_ch,,0000,0000,0000,,註：當發現有破壞遊戲平衡的\N疑似密技行為會立刻進行修正\N幾乎可以防止所有的遊戲異常\N和鑽系統漏洞的狀況發生。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,營運SAO的ARGUS公司...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被RECT收購
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是ARGUS的技術資產
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被RECT吸收且利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這裡面會有我的個人資料呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看一下爸爸的檔案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這的確是爸爸在SAO裡使用的角色檔案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儲存檔案的格式幾乎是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以兩個遊戲共通技能的熟練度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就直接覆蓋上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 二刀流沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道具...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像都損毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會被除錯程式檢測出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是全部丟棄比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:17.55,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,89)}警告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:17.55,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz2.583\pos(417,188)}您要消除全部道具嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 技能熟練度該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於技能的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要不被人類GM直接看見就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這、這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下可不是封弊者...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而真的是作弊者了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結衣現在是什麼樣的存在呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被歸類在輔助玩家用的模擬人格程式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名稱是「導航妖精」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:14:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我精靈時的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好癢哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是跟以前一樣有管理者權限嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能提供查詢與登入廣域地圖檔案而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜...妳媽媽或許也在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也在？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜在SAO遊戲結束之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有回到現實世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得到消息說在ALfheim世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人看見長很得像亞絲娜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我大致上知道她的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是...在世界樹那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概...就是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽...就在那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼會出現在這個什麼都沒有的森林裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來應該是被傳送到領地的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我也不知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許是位置情報損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者與附近訊息搞混了...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如讓我掉在世界樹附近就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這就是翅膀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼樣才能飛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有輔助搖桿的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請伸出左手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後做出握拳的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手往前拉便是上升
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往後倒便是下降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左右搖是旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按下按鈕是加速
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開按鈕則是減速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在翅膀發光的時候才可以飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛行一定時間後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須讓翅膀休息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我大致了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 離這裡最近的城鎮在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在西邊有一座叫「司伊魯班」的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是最近的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有玩家接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉、莉法！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 雷根！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要逃到風精靈領地...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷根 快避開！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真纏人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸？！ 我不行啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西格魯特他們也一定是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡量拖住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想辦法打倒一個！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我盡量...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶而也要讓我看看你帥氣的一面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去能贏！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別停下來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷根...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把錢和道具留下的話就放妳走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你裝什麼紳士啊 影宗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對手是女性讓我很興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺了她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就算死也要再拉一個人陪葬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不怕掉經驗值的傢伙就過來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個倔強的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,著陸失敗了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.54,0:20:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三個重戰士襲擊一個女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也太難看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個初心者竟然敢跑到這裡來！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就如你所願
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.25,0:21:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你幹掉吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉這些人應該沒關係吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這...這應該沒關係吧...
